Fit the Estimator Using Training Data

Train the estimator for self._train_steps steps, after waiting for delay_secs seconds. If self._train_steps is NULL, train forever.

# S3 method for tf_experiment
train(object, delay_secs = NULL, ...)

Arguments

object

A TensorFlow experiment object.
delay_secs

Start training after this many seconds.
...

Optional arguments passed to the estimator's train() method.

Value

The trained estimator.

See also

Other experiment methods: evaluate.tf_experiment, experiment.tf_estimator, train_and_evaluate.tf_experiment
